## DESIGN SYSTEM

Visual language: Clean, institutional, trustworthy. NOT startup-flashy.
Think: Stripe meets legal tech meets security infrastructure.

Colors (Tailwind sentinel.*):
- sentinel-navy:   #0F1B2D   (primary dark)
- sentinel-blue:   #1A3A5C   (secondary)
- sentinel-accent: #2563EB   (action blue)
- sentinel-green:  #059669   (verified / success)
- sentinel-amber:  #D97706   (pending / warning)
- sentinel-red:    #DC2626   (failed / error)
- sentinel-gray:   #F8FAFC   (page background)

Typography:
- Headings: Inter 700
- Body: Inter 400/500
- Code/hashes: JetBrains Mono
- font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums on all hash displays

Component patterns:
- Hash displays: font-hash class, truncated with expand, copy-to-clipboard
- Timestamps: always ISO 8601 — never relative ("2 hours ago")
- Status badges: colored dot + text, never emoji
- Verification status: VERIFIED (green) | PENDING (amber) | FAILED (red) | UNVERIFIED (gray)

